GAMEPAD 1:
A: Shoot One
X: Shoot All Macro
Y: Toggle Shooter
B: Reset Spindex Macro
Down: Toggle Speed
Left: One Ball Left
Up: Toggle LockOn
Right: One Ball Right
LeftBump: Spin In
RightBump: Spin Out
LeftTrig: Turret Manual Left
RightTrig: Turret Manual Right
LStX: Strafe
LStY: Movement
RStX: Turning
RStY: Turning
LStCl:
RStCl:
Back:
Start:


